# Sentry (iPix / amo-2b)

## Two products — do not conflate

| Product | What it does | Proof it works |
|---------|--------------|----------------|
| **Next.js SDK** (`@sentry/nextjs` in `app/`) | Runtime errors → Issues | Event in [amo-2b Issues](https://amo-2b.sentry.io/) |
| **Seer AI Code Review** | Predicts bugs on GitHub PRs | `seer-by-sentry[bot]` comments + optional Checks |

SDK install ≠ PR reviews. Missing Seer comments means the **GitHub app / Seer repo toggle**, not a missing DSN.

Docs: [Seer Code Review](https://docs.sentry.io/product/ai-in-sentry/seer/code-review/) · [Product page](https://sentry.io/product/seer/ai-code-review/) · [sentry-for-ai skill](https://github.com/getsentry/sentry-for-ai/blob/main/skills/sentry-pr-code-review/SKILL.md)

